channel.title: RSCFinale - Come join us in pking!
channel.description:
Welcome to [b]RSCFinale.[/b]
[b]RSCFinale[/b] is a [i]StorkPK-like[/i] server, estimated release date: 25/10/14.
[b]Starting Items[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/2oveO3e.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/razcRc8.png[/img]
[b]Starting Points[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/5D8jjeN.png[/img]
[b]Control Panel(Stats changing)[/b] Login to your [b]RSCFinanle[/b] character to change stats. [img]http://i.gyazo.com/d186bc7273e81ec6955edc6a57274a0d.png[/img]
[b]Add your starting points to get a quicker head start![/b] [img]http://i.gyazo.com/d17d6a96a121293bb732e00d6e195093.png[/img] [img]http://i.gyazo.com/fc45da91387ab2998de389a0a14d73c2.png[/img]
[b]Training[/b] Once you've added the starting points grab some food! [img]http://i.imgur.com/olpKnH6.png[/img] Head to the men's hut to gather points and coins to get started! [img]http://i.imgur.com/mRr5xXD.png[/img]
[b]More training areas[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/OyoiRiK.png[/img]
[b]Edgeville Dungeon[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Gt5VCIz.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/R1dyDZL.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/hnt4jRM.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/G3CbhPj.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/7FOCiSU.png[/img] [b]Other areas include the wilderness, please explore to find out more.[/b]
[b]For more information check us out at [url=http://www.RSCFinale.net]www.rscfinale.net[/url]
